    <p>We have an opportunity to finally fix Drupal file extensions once and forever in <a href="https://drupal.org/node/7269" title="https://drupal.org/node/7269">https://drupal.org/node/7269</a></p>
<p>The planned move from PSR0 to PSR4 in <a href="https://drupal.org/node/2247991" title="https://drupal.org/node/2247991">https://drupal.org/node/2247991</a> will break many/most patches in the queue.<br />
Syncing the rename of our procedural code files with the change above minimizes disruption and brings similar DX gains for D8.</p>
<p>Drop by and provide your feedback on this issue.</p>
